#. <section class="sutta" id="sn45.141"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn45.141-145:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 45"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 45"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.141-145:0.2"
msgid "11. Appamādapeyyālavagga"
msgstr "11. Abbreviated Texts on Diligence"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 141–​145. Kūṭādisutta → rājasuttāni (bj) | rājā (pts1)
msgctxt "sn45.141-145:0.3"
msgid "141–​145. Kūṭādisutta"
msgstr "141–145. A Roof Peak"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn45.141-145:1.1"
msgid "“Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, kūṭāgārassa yā kāci gopānasiyo sabbā tā kūṭaṅgamā kūṭaninnā kūṭasamosaraṇā; kūṭaṃ tāsaṃ aggamakkhāyati;"
msgstr "“Mendicants, the rafters of a bungalow all lean to the peak, slope to the peak, and meet at the peak, so the peak is said to be the topmost of them all."

msgctxt "sn45.141-145:1.2"
msgid "evameva kho, bhikkhave … pe …"
msgstr "In the same way …”"

msgctxt "sn45.141-145:1.3"
msgid "(yathā heṭṭhimasuttantaṃ, evaṃ vitthāretabbaṃ.)"
msgstr "(This should be told in full as in the previous discourse.)"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn45.141-145:1.4"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli5.44"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn45.141-145:2.1"
msgid "“Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, ye keci mūlagandhā, kāḷānusāriyaṃ tesaṃ aggamakkhāyati;"
msgstr "“Of all kinds of fragrant root, spikenard is said to be the best. …”"

msgctxt "sn45.141-145:2.2"
msgid "evameva kho, bhikkhave … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn45.141-145:2.3"
msgid "catutthaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn45.141-145:3.1"
msgid "“Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, ye keci sāragandhā, lohitacandanaṃ tesaṃ aggamakkhāyati;"
msgstr "“Of all kinds of fragrant heartwood, red sandalwood is said to be the best. …”"

msgctxt "sn45.141-145:3.2"
msgid "evameva kho, bhikkhave … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn45.141-145:3.3"
msgid "pañcamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn45.141-145:4.1"
msgid "“Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, ye keci pupphagandhā, vassikaṃ tesaṃ aggamakkhāyati;"
msgstr "“Of all kinds of fragrant flower, jasmine is said to be the best. …”"

msgctxt "sn45.141-145:4.2"
msgid "evameva kho, bhikkhave … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn45.141-145:4.3"
msgid "chaṭṭhaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "sn45.141-145:5.1"
msgid "“Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, ye keci kuṭṭarājāno, sabbe te rañño cakkavattissa anuyantā bhavanti, rājā tesaṃ cakkavatti aggamakkhāyati;"
msgstr "“All lesser kings are vassals of a wheel-turning monarch, so the wheel-turning monarch is said to be the foremost of them all. …”"

msgctxt "sn45.141-145:5.2"
msgid "evameva kho, bhikkhave … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn45.141-145:5.3"
msgid "sattamaṃ."
msgstr ""
